<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <title>J-Trip Advisor</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <style>
        /* 커스텀 스타일 정의 (カスタムスタイル定義) */
        .badge-score { font-size: 0.9em; }

        /* 삭제 버튼 스타일 조정: 사용자 실수 방지를 위해 너무 눈에 띄지 않게 처리 */
        /* 削除ボタンスタイルの調整: ユーザーの操作ミスを防ぐため、目立ちすぎないように処理 */
        .btn-delete {
            line-height: 1;
            padding: 0 5px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container pt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-5">🇯🇵 J-Trip Advisor</h1>

    <div class="row">
        {{#places}}
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
                            <h4 class="card-title font-weight-bold mb-0">{{name}}</h4>
                            <span class="badge badge-warning text-white shadow-sm" style="font-size: 1.0rem;">
                                ⭐ {{averageScore}}
                            </span>
                        </div>

                        <p class="card-text">{{description}}</p>
                        <hr>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <h6 class="text-muted mb-2">📝 여행자 리뷰 & AI 점수</h6>
                            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">

                                {{#reviews}}
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center px-0">
                                        <span class="text-dark">{{content}}</span>

                                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                            <span class="badge badge-primary badge-pill badge-score mr-2">{{sentimentScore}}점</span>

                                            <form action="/review/delete" method="post" style="margin: 0;">
                                                <input type="hidden" name="reviewId" value="{{id}}">
                                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger border-0 btn-delete" onclick="return confirm('정말 삭제하시겠습니까?');">
                                                    &times;
                                                </button>
                                            </form>
                                        </div>
                                    </li>
                                {{/reviews}}

                                {{^reviews}}
                                    <li class="list-group-item text-muted small px-0">
                                        아직 작성된 리뷰가 없습니다.<br>첫 번째 리뷰를 남겨보세요!
                                        (まだ作成されたレビューがありません。<br>最初のレビューを残してみてください！)
                                    </li>
                                {{/reviews}}
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <form action="/review" method="post">
                            <input type="hidden" name="placeId" value="{{id}}">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <textarea name="content" class="form-control" placeholder="리뷰를 남겨주세요 (일본어)" rows="2" required></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark btn-block">리뷰 등록 / AI 분석</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/places}}

        {{^places}}
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <p>등록된 관광지가 없습니다. DB에 데이터를 추가해주세요!</p>
                <p>(登録された観光地がありません。DBにデータを追加してください！)</p>
            </div>
        {{/places}}
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>